Difference between ArrayList and LinkedList?

            ArrayList                                       LinkedList
 1.Arraylist is the best choice                 1.LinkedList is the best choice 
   if our frequesnt operation is retrieval        if our frequesnt operation is insertion or deletion
   
 2. Data Structure for Arraylist is growable    2. Data structure for Linked List is Double Linked List
    Array
 3. Arraylist implements RandomAccess Interface 3. Linked List doesn't implements RandomAccess Interface